# ğŸ§  AI Meeting Notes Summarizer

This project is a **Streamlit web app** that extracts **action items** and **key summaries** from meeting transcripts using state-of-the-art **NLP models**. Users can either paste a transcript or upload a `.mp3`/`.wav` file to get instant summaries.

